#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn21.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn21.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 21 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 21 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn21.11:0.2"
msgid "1. Bhikkhuvagga "
msgstr "1. Monks "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 11. Mahākappinasutta → kappino (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn21.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Mahākappinasutta "
msgstr "11. With Mahākappina "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn21.11:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn21.11:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā mahākappino yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami. "
msgstr "Then Venerable Mahākappina went to see the Buddha. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn21.11:1.3"
msgid "Addasā kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ mahākappinaṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. "
msgstr "The Buddha saw him coming off in the distance, "

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.4"
msgid "Disvāna bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "and addressed the mendicants: "

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.5"
msgid "“passatha no tumhe, bhikkhave, etaṃ bhikkhuṃ āgacchantaṃ odātakaṃ tanukaṃ tuṅganāsikan”ti? "
msgstr "“Mendicants, do you you see that monk coming—white, thin, with a pointy nose?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn21.11:1.6"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn21.11:1.7"
msgid "“Eso kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu mahiddhiko mahānubhāvo. "
msgstr "“That mendicant is very mighty and powerful. It’s not easy to find an attainment that he has not already attained. "

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.8"
msgid "Na ca sā samāpatti sulabharūpā yā tena bhikkhunā asamāpannapubbā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn21.11:1.9"
msgid "Yassa catthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti tadanuttaraṃ brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī”ti. "
msgstr "And he has realized the supreme end of the spiritual path in this very life. He lives having achieved with his own insight the goal for which gentlemen rightly go forth from the lay life to homelessness.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn21.11:2.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn21.11:2.2"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvāna sugato athāparaṃ etadavoca satthā: "
msgstr "Then the Holy One, the Teacher, went on to say: "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.1"
msgid "“Khattiyo seṭṭho janetasmiṃ, "
msgstr "“The aristocrat is best of those people "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.2"
msgid "ye gottapaṭisārino; "
msgstr "who take clan as the standard. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.3"
msgid "Vijjācaraṇasampanno, "
msgstr "But one accomplished in knowledge and conduct "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:3.4"
msgid "so seṭṭho devamānuse. "
msgstr "is best of gods and humans. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.1"
msgid "Divā tapati ādicco, "
msgstr "The sun shines by day, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.2"
msgid "rattimābhāti candimā; "
msgstr "the moon glows at night, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.3"
msgid "Sannaddho khattiyo tapati, "
msgstr "the aristocrat shines in armor, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.4"
msgid "jhāyī tapati brāhmaṇo; "
msgstr "and the brahmin shines in absorption. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Atha sabbamahorattiṃ → atha sabbamahorattaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.5"
msgid "Atha sabbamahorattiṃ, "
msgstr "But all day and all night, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.6"
msgid "buddho tapati tejasā”ti. "
msgstr "the Buddha shines with glory.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn21.11:4.7"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
